description: The SPDR Bloomberg High Yield Bond ETF seeks to provide investment results that, before fees and expenses, correspond generally to the price and yield performance of the Bloomberg High Yield Very Liquid Index (the "Index")Seeks to provide a diversified exposure to US dollar-denominated high yield corporate bonds with above-average liquidityA more cost efficient way to implement a high yield exposure than via individual bondsRebalanced on the last business day of the month
name: SPDR Bloomberg High Yield Bond ETF
